# Samay Raina Fan Website 🎤

A modern Netflix-inspired fan website dedicated to **Samay Raina**.

Checkout: https://ar33b-shola.github.io

## About

This project is a completely fan-made website created for the Indian comedy king, chess streamer and entertainer **Samay Raina**.

The website is built using HTML, CSS and JavaScript.

## Tech Stack

- HTML5
- CSS3
- Vanilla JavaScript



## Why I Built This

I'm a huge fan of Samay Raina and wanted to create something unique instead of another ordinary fan page.

## Run Locally

bash
git clone https://github.com/ar33b-shola/ar33b-shola.github.io

cd ar33b-shola.github.io
open index.html / start index.html

